# Private per-client notes — see INTEGRATION.md Pattern 4
# These patterns let operators keep private local annotations alongside
# client folders without shipping them in any public release of the CD.

clients/*/PRIVATE-*.md
clients/*/*.private.md
**/PRIVATE-*.md
**/*.private.md

# Local config (operator-specific URLs, workspace IDs, etc.)
local-config.md
*.local.md
